trong\u003eApple Music\u003c/strong\u003e. Matching the songs on the destination will take a while, but not too long. Soon, my Apple Music playlists appeared—names intact, with the sync date appended at the end.\u003c/p\u003e    \n                \n    \n    \n    \n                \n    \n                \n        \n                                                            \n                                                                                                                        \n                            \n    \n    \n    \u003cdiv data-img-url=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/playlists-on-apple-music.jpg\" data-modal-id=\"single-image-modal\" data-modal-container-id=\"single-image-modal-container\" data-img-caption=\"\u0026#34;\u0026#34;\"\u003e\n\n            \n\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\n        \u003cpicture\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 1024px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/playlists-on-apple-music.jpg?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=1\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/playlists-on-apple-music.jpg?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=1\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/playlists-on-apple-music.jpg?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=1\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/playlists-on-apple-music.jpg?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=1\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 481px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/playlists-on-apple-music.jpg?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=1\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/playlists-on-apple-music.jpg?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=1\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/playlists-on-apple-music.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/playlists-on-apple-music.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                \u003cimg width=\"1598\" height=\"697\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"Playlists on Apple Music\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/playlists-on-apple-music.jpg\" src=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/playlists-on-apple-music.jpg\"/\u003e\n    \u003c/picture\u003e\n                                    \n    \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eTo be honest, I’d prefer if the sync date was in the description instead of the title. Apple Music’s playlist covers are already ugly, and having the date cluttering the name doesn’t help. But that’s a minor nitpick.\u003c/p\u003e    \n\n\u003cdiv id=\"custom_block_14\"\u003e\n\n        \n            \u003cp\u003ePlaylists.cloud doesn\u0026#39;t import or export playlist covers. It\u0026#39;s a minor inconvenience, but you\u0026#39;ll have to manually update them after syncing.\u003c/p\u003e\n    \n        \n    \u003c/div\u003e\u003ch2 id=\"keeping-playlists-updated\"\u003e\n                        Keeping Playlists Updated\n               \u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eSince Spotify is better for discovering new music, I first update my playlists. That means my Apple Music versions will eventually become outdated. Thankfully, once your playlists are imported into Playlists.cloud, you don’t have to reimport them.\u003c/p\u003e    \n                \n    \n    \n    \n                \n    \n                \n        \n                                                            \n                                                                                                                        \n                            \n    \n    \n    \u003cdiv data-img-url=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/playlist-options-in-playlists-cloud.jpg\" data-modal-id=\"single-image-modal\" data-modal-container-id=\"single-image-modal-container\" data-img-caption=\"\u0026#34;\u0026#34;\"\u003e\n\n            \n\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\n        \u003cpicture\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 1024px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/playlist-options-in-playlists-cloud.jpg?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=1\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/playlist-options-in-playlists-cloud.jpg?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=1\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/playlist-options-in-playlists-cloud.jpg?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=1\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/playlist-options-in-playlists-cloud.jpg?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=1\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 481px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/playlist-options-in-playlists-cloud.jpg?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=1\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/playlist-options-in-playlists-cloud.jpg?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=1\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/playlist-options-in-playlists-cloud.jpg?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=1\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/playlist-options-in-playlists-cloud.jpg?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=1\"/\u003e\n                \u003cimg width=\"967\" height=\"342\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"Playlist options in Playlists.cloud\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/playlist-options-in-playlists-cloud.jpg\" src=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/playlist-options-in-playlists-cloud.jpg\"/\u003e\n    \u003c/picture\u003e\n                                    \n    \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eAll you have to do is open the website once in a while, click \u003cstrong\u003eResynchronize\u003c/strong\u003e, then click \u003cstrong\u003eExport to Provider\u003c/strong\u003e, and Apple Music catches up. That’s it—no hassle, no limits, and no extra cost. \u003c/p\u003e    \n\n\u003cdiv id=\"custom_block_19\"\u003e\n\n        \n            \u003cp\u003eAnother great feature of Playlists.cloud is that it lets you export your playlists as CSV and JSON files. This means you can keep an offline backup of your entire music library.\u003c/p\u003e\n    \n        \n    \u003c/div\u003e        \n    \n                    \n                        \n                \n    \n                                        \n    \n        \n    \n        \n                \n        \n    \u003cdiv data-include-community-rating=\"false\" id=\"1a18-46c8-adb206bfef83\" data-nosnippet=\"\"\u003e\n        \n        \n                        \t                \n\t\t\u003ca href=\"https://www.makeuseof.com/how-to-improve-spotify-recommendations/\"\u003e\n\t\n\t\u003cdiv data-img-url=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/a-headphone-with-a-phone-playing-music-on-spotify.jpg\" data-modal-id=\"single-image-modal\" data-modal-container-id=\"single-image-modal-container\" data-img-caption=\"\u0026#34;\u0026#34;\"\u003e\n\n            \n\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\n        \u003cpicture\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 1024px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/a-headphone-with-a-phone-playing-music-on-spotify.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=422\u0026amp;h=268\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/a-headphone-with-a-phone-playing-music-on-spotify.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=422\u0026amp;h=268\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/a-headphone-with-a-phone-playing-music-on-spotify.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=310\u0026amp;h=220\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/a-headphone-with-a-phone-playing-music-on-spotify.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=310\u0026amp;h=220\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 481px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/a-headphone-with-a-phone-playing-music-on-spotify.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=720\u0026amp;h=400\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/a-headphone-with-a-phone-playing-music-on-spotify.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=720\u0026amp;h=400\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/a-headphone-with-a-phone-playing-music-on-spotify.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=432\u0026amp;h=260\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/a-headphone-with-a-phone-playing-music-on-spotify.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=432\u0026amp;h=260\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                \u003cimg width=\"2100\" height=\"1400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"A headphone with a phone playing music on Spotify.\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/a-headphone-with-a-phone-playing-music-on-spotify.jpg\" src=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/a-headphone-with-a-phone-playing-music-on-spotify.jpg\"/\u003e\n    \u003c/picture\u003e\n                \n    \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\t\t\u003c/a\u003e\n\t\n\n        \n                    \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-field=\"label\"\u003eRelated\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\n\n                \n                 \n                \t\n\u003ch5\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t        \t\t\t\t\n\t\t\u003ca href=\"https://www.makeuseof.com/how-to-improve-spotify-recommendations/\" title=\"7 Ways I\u0026#39;ve Improved My Spotify Recommendations\" target=\"_blank\"\u003e\n\t\t\t7 Ways I\u0026#39;ve Improved My Spotify Recommendations\n\t\t\u003c/a\u003e\n\t\u003c/h5\u003e\n\n                                                    \n                \t\t\t\u003cp\u003eThese are the features and methods I\u0026#39;ve used to make sure that I get better recommendations from Spotify.\u003c/p\u003e\n\t\n\n                    \n\n\n                \n                \n                \n                \n\n                \n                \n                \n                \t\n\n\n                \n\n                \n                \n                \n            \u003c/div\u003e\n                \n        \n        \n        \n            \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eIt took me forever to find it, but Playlists.cloud turned out to be exactly what I needed. Now, I don’t think twice about which service I’m using—my music is everywhere I want it to be.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
